These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, water, milk, mirinda
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, martial-arts, time-travel, epic, animation
There are 5 different nationalities: spanish, indian, japanese, german, polish
5 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, fish, cat, hamster
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the spanish is on the left of the japanese##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is between the indian and the person watching animation movies##2
12. the german is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
13. the polish is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | cola        | iced-tea | mirinda     | water   | milk |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | martial-arts      | epic | animation   | scientific    |
| Nationality   | german  | indian     | spanish | japanese | polish  |
| Pet           | horse | fish      | hamster     | cat   | mouse     |

