.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, baking, dancing, camping
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, metal, reggae, gospel, electronic
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, american, canadian, british, egyptian
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, car, ship, bike, van
 1. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the american##1
 5. the person driving the car is between the japanese and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the canadian is the fan of gospel##1
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of metal##1
11. the canadian is the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person driving the car is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | dancing | collecting | camping    | video-games  | baking    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | metal       | reggae      | folk | gospel        |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | american     | japanese    | british  | canadian     |
| Transport     | ship    | car | van | bike | boat |

