.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, baking, gardening, drawing, card-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, musical, zombie, sports, time-travel
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, disco, house, d&b, folk
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, skiing, sailing, climbing
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the fan of disco##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of d&b is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 9. the fan of house is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person watching sports movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the fan of folk##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | chess | card-games     | gardening   | baking   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | musical | action | sports | zombie        |
| Music-Genre   | house      | disco      | d&b       | folk       | trance       |
| Sport         | golf | climbing  | sailing    | snowboarding    | skiing        |

