.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: raspberry, avocado, lettuce, banana, cabbage
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, gospel-climbing, chess, photography, camping
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, hip-hop, pop, d&b, gospel
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, chinese, russian, italian, american
 1. the chinese is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 4. the american is between the fan of d&b and the person eating banana##2
 5. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the russian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of gospel is in the middle##1
10. the fan of d&b is the nigerian##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
12. the nigerian is on the right of the fan of pop##1
13. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | cabbage  | lettuce     | banana   | avocado     | raspberry |
| Hobby         | camping | collecting    | chess  | photography | gospel-climbing   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop        | trance    | gospel     | pop     | d&b    |
| Nationality   | chinese    | russian | italian | american | nigerian   |

