.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, tea, cola, fanta
There 5 different types of food: garlic, pepper, grapefruit, mango, peas
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, pilot, coach, fisherman, journalist
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, badminton, swimming, sailing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the videographer##1
 2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person eating garlic##2
 5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the pilot##1
 8. the journalist is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking water is on the right of the videographer##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
12. the fisherman is on the left of the videographer##1
13. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | cola       | fanta       | 7up   | tea      | water    |
| Food       | peas | mango        | garlic       | grapefruit       | pepper |
| Job        | journalist     | pilot        | fisherman | videographer        | coach  |
| Sport      | sailing | swimming | surfing      | water-polo | badminton  |

