.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel, comedy, martial-arts, disaster
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, thai, japanese, canadian, egyptian
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, cycling, cricket, tea-polo, basketball
 1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the japanese##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person drinking tea is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's sport is cycling##2
 7. the person who's sport is cricket is the egyptian##1
 8. the thai is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the japanese##1
10. the person who's sport is tea-polo is on the far right##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's sport is cycling##2
12. the person drinking juice is on the right of the canadian##1
13. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | milk  | tea      | mirinda   | juice   | hot-chocolate   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | martial-arts   | comedy   | time-travel | romance     |
