 1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the goat is the person driving the bus##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the malaysian##2
 5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
 7. the pakistani is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the british is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the fish is the pakistani##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the right of the russian##1
12. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is reading##1
13. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
