 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is photography##2
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | water       | lemonade    | coffee | milk  | fanta        |
| Hobby       | board-games | cooking | photography  | skydiving | gardening    |
| Sport       | parkour        | volleyball   | biathlon  | weightlifting   | rugby |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | helicopter      | subway      | scooter | tram  |

