.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, lemonade, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, electrician, dancer, journalist, freelancer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, drama, western, disaster, romance
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, rock, funk, r&b, folk
 1. the fan of funk is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 2. the journalist is between the person watching western movies and the dancer##2
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the journalist##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the freelancer and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of r&b is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the freelancer##1
10. the security-guard is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
11. the dancer is the person watching drama movies##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea      | fanta         | hot-chocolate      | lemonade | soy-milk     |
| Job           | electrician | dancer | journalist | freelancer    | security-guard  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | drama    | spy | western    | romance |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | rock        | pop   | r&b    | folk     |

