.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: traind-games, cooking, collecting, woodworking, filmmaking
There are 5 different nationalities: french, spanish, malaysian, canadian, polish
5 different pets are kept: frog, horse, rat, chinchilla, hamster
The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, train, skateboard, motorbike, snowmobile
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the canadian is on the left of the spanish##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the horse is between the french and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the french is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person driving the roller and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is traind-games##2
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is traind-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is traind-games is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | collecting | woodworking   | cooking      | traind-games |
| Nationality   | french   | canadian    | spanish | polish | malaysian      |
| Pet           | rat | horse    | frog       | chinchilla     | hamster      |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile        | roller  | train        | motorbike    |

