.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, camping, gardening, jazz-climbing, writing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, mystery, disaster, zombie, crime
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, soul, r&b, dubstep, jazz
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, brazilian, argentine, turkish, japanese
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 2. the person watching crime movies is between the turkish and the fan of jazz##2
 3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is between the japanese and the fan of r&b##2
 6. the japanese is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of dubstep##1
 8. the person who's hobby is jazz-climbing is the fan of soul##1
 9. the dutch is the fan of soul##1
10. the person who's hobby is jazz-climbing is on the right of the argentine##1
11. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | gardening    | writing  | camping  | fishing      | jazz-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | crime   | zombie | disaster | family   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | classical    | jazz    | dubstep       | soul         |
| Nationality   | turkish  | brazilian | japanese    | argentine     | dutch      |

 